Tab 1 — Executive Summary
Purpose: The "big reveal" — where does the user stand overall?
Key Elements:

Hero headline synthesizing maturity, readiness, and dimension patterns
Two score cards (Maturity % + Band, Readiness % + Band)
2×2 Strategic Matrix showing quadrant positioning (Scale-Ready Zone, Structural Misalignment, etc.)
"What Good Looks Like at This Stage" (stage-anchoring content)
"What Advancing to the Next Stage Requires" (forward-looking frame)

