Purpose: Systems-level insight — how do the 5 dimensions behave?
Key Elements:

Radial/pentagon chart visualizing dimension maturity (business shape metaphor)
5 expandable dimension cards (maturity %, readiness %, stage-fit, brief synthesis)
System-Level Analysis section (cross-dimensional patterns: Strengths, Constraints, Opportunities)

